Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:53.35,Bottom,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill him! I'll kill him…\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:53.35,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,‎ブッ殺す！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:55.98,Bottom,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fucking--\N
