Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.44,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,‎（注入音）\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:00.44,Bottom,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:00.49,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,‎大丈夫か？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.11,Bottom,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go save Lucy.\N
