Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:39.40,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,‎（レベッカ）\N‎うおおっ また始まったぞ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.40,Bottom,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go again!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:42.86,Bottom,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!\N
